            <title><![CDATA[Original XCOM Creator Thinks Switch 2 Mouse Controls Have Big Strategy-Game Potential]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/original-xcom-creator-thinks-switch-2-mouse-controls-have-big-strategy-game-potential/1100-6531445/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
